Title: Toy Story 3: Trailer
Comment:
I grew up with Toy Story, and to see Andy all grown up and going to college, just like me, brings tears to my eyes. I feel I am going to cry throughout this movie like no other movie in my life.

At first, I honestly thought Toy Story 2 was ENOUGH, but now I see. It's pretty much the tale of every growing boy or girl, when they must leave childhood behind. I just didn't think Andy would be one of them..... <=[

Nevertheless, this will be one of the best movies I will ever see. Period.
